--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages mtr.

Mtr is a network diagnostic tool that combines ping and traceroute into one
program. Mtr provides two interfaces: an ncurses interface, useful for using
Mtr from a telnet session; and a GTK+ interface for X (provided in the mtr-gtk
package).

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: mtr
       mtr_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: mtr
       mtr_state: 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  mtr_state
    Description: Control the state of the role.
    Implemented: 0.1
    Required   : False
    Value      : Predetermined
    Type       : String
    Default    : 'install'
    Options    :
      Install: 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
      Remove : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'

